## Commands

### cc-sdd (Spec Driven Development)

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `/kiro:steering` | Collect project context |
| `/kiro:spec-init <feature>` | Initialize feature workspace |
| `/kiro:spec-requirements <feature>` | Define requirements (EARS format) |
| `/kiro:spec-design <feature>` | Architecture design |
| `/kiro:spec-tasks <feature>` | Task breakdown |
| `/kiro:spec-impl <feature> <task-ids>` | Implementation |

### ECC (Everything Claude Code)

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `/ecc-bootstrap` | Install safety + design knowledge |
| `/ecc-configure` | Install implementation components |
| `/ecc-evolve` | Continuous improvement + ECC sync |

## Workflow

```
/ecc-bootstrap → /kiro:steering → spec-init → spec-requirements
→ spec-design → spec-tasks → /ecc-configure → /tdd → /ecc-evolve
```

## Git Workflow

- Conventional commits: `feat:`, `fix:`, `refactor:`, `docs:`, `test:`
- Feature branches from `main`
- PRs required for merge

